reviews.text: They have absolutely fantastic vegetarian burger and pizza. The best Italian restaurant in Tai Po. Waiter/ waitress are also friendly. Its our favourite restaurant.
Lunch is pretty good for the price. Mediocre service in general.
Delicious western food at reasonable price
Been a regular for several years and this shop never disappoints. The food is awesome and reasonable priced, highly recommended.

Small but cozy cafe that serves delicious western food. Spaghetti and pizzas are very well served. The lunch set menus offers different food choices ranging from baked rice, pasta to burgers. And they are served with a great variety of drinks. Iced chocolate, rose coffee and iced lemon teas are highly recommended. All food are reasonably priced. This is a must try restaurant in tai wo.

reviews.text:
👍🏻極推大埔區算好吃的羊排（當天沒有吃）
👍🏻極推非常多口味選擇的好喝巧克力
👍🏻當天吃了2人晚餐，$198，2前菜2主菜，份量十分足夠，左加右加埋單$268，相對食物質數，此價格非常滿意。
👍🏻薯條＋$8芝士醬*喜愛芝士必加，十分好吃有驚喜。
👍🏻三重芝士帶子意粉，與女兒一致表示，雖然已經很飽但還是會想一直吃
❤️此餐廳非常邪惡，我們結論一個月最多只能去一次🤭🤭🤭
They have absolutely fantastic vegetarian burger and pizza. The best Italian restaurant in Tai Po. Waiter/ waitress are also friendly. Its our favourite restaurant.
款式多樣化的西餐廳，味道不錯，價錢尚算大眾化
Lunch is pretty good for the price. Mediocre service in general.

今日星期日去食，落完單 意粉兩分鐘就到
一早整定唔緊要！成隻碟邊都係水，有無搞錯？洗完唔抹乾，但至比客前至少都抹一抹掛？
